706799f-a.title: Brooklyn: Skidmore Lane - Rockaway Parkway
706799f-a.text:
Skidmore Lane, south side, between Rockaway Parkway (right) and East
98th Street (left), showing several old homes.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
